  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00001",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵大上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00002",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "越热越出汗，越冷越打颤。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00003",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "我，赵大的便是，在这定远县东大洼居住。不幸父母双亡，是我夫妻二人，烧窑度日。这些日子，买卖不好，不免将老婆唤出，做些个盆子罐子，烧烧，好到集镇上去卖。老婆哪里？",
      "text_length": 80
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00004",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵妻上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00005",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "text": "自幼儿在东庄居住，嫁了个汉子是窑户。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00006",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "text": "我说当家的，叫我干什么？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00007",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "我说这些日子，无有什么生意，叫你出来，咱们做点活儿，我好到集镇上去，卖钱使用。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00008",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "text": "言之有理，你我到后面去做活便了。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00009",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "夫妻二人把后窑进，取点柴火烧瓦盆。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00010",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵大、赵妻同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00011",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘世昌上，刘升随上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00012",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "一日离家一日深，好似孤雁宿寒林。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00013",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "卑人，刘世昌，乃四川华阳人氏。前奉母命，进京贩卖绸缎，是我主仆二人，讨清帐目，转回家园。刘升，带路。",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00014",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "自从那年离乡井，思会双亲常挂在心。主仆贸易三年整，讨清帐目转回家门。走过了多少州县郡，晓行夜宿马不留停。一霎时乌云起天盖定，",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00015",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "倾盆大雨洒淋淋。叫刘升与爷把路引，寻找旅店把身存。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00016",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘世昌、刘升同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00017",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众鬼同上，判官上，堆鬼，同下。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00018",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘世昌、刘升同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00019",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "急急忙忙往前奔，不觉来到一窑门。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00020",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "来此窑门，刘升上前言道，你我在此借宿一宵，明日早行。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00021",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘升"
      ],
      "text": "这我会。我说有人么，走出一个来！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00022",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵大上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00023",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "是谁呀？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00024",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘升"
      ],
      "text": "我们要到你们这来睡觉啦！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00025",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "你这小子，满嘴胡说八道！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00026",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘升"
      ],
      "text": "什么小子？你才是小子呐！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00027",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "吓，大哥请了。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00028",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "请啦，你们是干什么的？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00029",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "我乃行路之人，天降大雨，无有旅店，欲想在大哥处，借宿一宵，明日早行。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00030",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "这才是会说话的呐。这个不要紧，请到窑里坐吧。我与你牵着马。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00031",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "这就不敢，请。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00032",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "你看你们的衣裳，都淋湿啦，快脱下来，我与你晾晾吧。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00033",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "有劳了。请问大哥尊姓大名？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00034",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "在下，姓赵，哥儿一个，人都叫我赵老大。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00035",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "原来是赵大哥。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00036",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "请问客人尊姓吓？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00037",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "卑人刘世昌，乃四川华阳县人氏。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00038",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "但不知作何买卖？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00039",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "贩卖绸缎为生。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00040",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "原来是大买卖。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00041",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "小本钱。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00042",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "好说好说。我说你们还没有吃饭吧？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00043",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "这……前途用过了。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00044",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "得啦，得啦，哪用过？咱们都不是外人，我也没有什么好吃的，也不过粗菜粗饭而已，等我与你烫酒去。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00045",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "有劳了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00046",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "慢着，我看这位客人，他行李里头，沉甸甸的，八成银子不少。我想我烧窑一辈子，也发不了财，不免将他害死，这银子都是我的啦。就是这个主意，老婆这来。",
      "text_length": 71
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00047",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵妻上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00048",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "text": "来了来了。当家的什么事？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00049",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "老婆，咱们要发财！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00050",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "text": "发什么财？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00051",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "刚才来了二位客人，是一主一仆，乃是卖绸缎的大客商，他行李里头，全是银子，我想把他害了，这银子都是咱们的啦！",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00052",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "text": "害人我可不会呀！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00053",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "别嚷，别嚷！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00054",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "text": "你说害人，怎么个害法吓？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00055",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "他们没有吃饭呐，你与他安排点酒饭，我把酒里头，与他下上点耗子药，他们吃了，不到一个时辰，管保他就跷缏子。",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00056",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "text": "这个，我倒能办得了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00057",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵妻下。赵妻托盘子上，下毒药，赵妻下。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00058",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "酒钣到啦，二位请用吧。来来来，我与你们斟上！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00059",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "有劳了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00060",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "好一个赵大哥多慷慨，一霎时酒饭摆上来。初次相逢承恩爱，借宿一霄理不该。明日里定要多谢拜，昏昏沉沉倒卧在土台。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00061",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "看他二人已经醉啦，待我将门倒锁上，咱们明个见。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00062",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵大下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00063",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "时才朦胧将睡倒，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00064",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘世昌"
      ],
      "text": "一霎时心中似火烧。是是是来明白了，中了赵大计笼牢。回头便把刘升叫，奴才一命赴阴曹。眼望着华阳县高声叫，爹娘吓！一命定然赴阴曹！",
      "text_length": 63
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00065",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘世昌死。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00066",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘升"
      ],
      "text": "时才间醉酒将合眼，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00067",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘升"
      ],
      "text": "我心中好似刀来穿。是是是来我知道了，中了他娘的巧机关！眼望着华阳县高声喊，我的妈妈呀！",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00068",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘升死。赵大、赵妻同上。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00069",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "天亮了，咱们去看看。没有什么动静，光景是死啦。待我开开门，喝，两人死了一对。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00070",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "text": "这两个死尸怎么办呐，抬出去埋了吧。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00071",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "不好，不好，倘若被人看见，那不是白做了活儿啦吗？有啦，有啦，咱们把他二人尸首，剁成肉酱，和在泥里，烧成了盆子，就是神仙也不能找寻着！",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00072",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "text": "好，等我拿刀去。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00073",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "来，咱们动手吧！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00074",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵妻"
      ],
      "text": "当家的，你看画上那个判官，他拿两个眼睛瞪我。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00075",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "他瞪你，待我把他的眼睛与他剜了去！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00076",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵大剜判官眼。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00077",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "得啦，咱们这可发财啦，赶紧叫泥瓦匠，先盖起房子来再说！正是：",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00078",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "赵大"
      ],
      "text": "禹门三激浪，平地一声雷。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00079",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵大、赵妻同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013006_e00080",
      "play_id": "01013006",
      "scene_id": "01013006_s05",
